eNCA's Nobesuthu Hejana has more details. Courtesy #DStv403 CAPE TOWN - Residents of Masiphumelele informal settlement in Cape Town are reeling from a devastating fire. The fire has destroyed over a hundred homes, leaving hundreds of people homeless. READ: R10m to extinguish 75 fires in 7 days No fatalities have been reported. eNCA reporter, Nobesuthu Hejana shares more details.